This User Agreement is subject to change.</p>
<h3>Conditions of Use</h3>
<p>Users may copy or distribute AHAD resources of parts thereof and/or use them in derivative works provided the following conditions are met:
<ol>
<li>The resource Creators (as identified on the Resource Record) are properly acknowledged with a full bibliographic citation and/or other appropriate attribution, and AHAD is identified as the archival source.</li>
<li>In the case of redistribution, the license terms of the resource must be included along with the citation of the Contributors and AHAD (as above).</li>
<li>All other terms of the license identified on the Resource Record are met.</li>
<li>Resources obtained through AHAD may not be used in ways that could lead, or could be reasonably expected to lead, directly or indirectly, to damage to the archaeological record.</li>
<li>The User acknowledges that neither La Trobe University, its sponsors and associates, nor those individuals and institutions providing content through AHAD, guarantee the accuracy or usability of the content and users further agree that they may not hold any of these parties liable for any direct or consequential damage arising from their use of AHAD or its content.</li>
</ol>
<p>Depositors may publish any Resource to AHAD provided the following conditions are met:</p>
<ol>
<li>The Rights Holder has authorised the publication and is identified on the Resource Record.</li>
<li>The information is, to the best of the Depositor’s knowledge: accurate, of relevance to historical archaeology in the Australasia region.</li>
<li>Reasonable efforts have been made to notify the Creators of the Resource of the Depositor’s intention to publish.</li>
<li>The Depositor acknowledges that AHAD reserves the right to access the Record for administrative purposes and to edit Keywords, if required.</li></ol></p>
